This directory describes the implementation of an LR parser for
Oberon (http://www.oberon.ethz.ch) quite a simple language in the line of Pascal and Modula-2.

The files:
	tests	        Directory containing some Oberon sources
	doc             Directory containing the language report and EBNF
	README

Exercises:
  - Implement an Oberon parser, i.e. write the files
    - oberon.scan       Scanner
    - oberon.pars	Parser
    - main.c            main() function
    - Makefile		add rules for generating, compli8ng and cleaning the sources
      			add rules to run the test suite tests/*
			add test files of your own.

  - Define an AST representing the Oberon, i.e. write
    - oberon.ast

  - Implement construction opf the AST, i.e. extend
    - oberon.pars
    - Makefile

